These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: cola, juice, lemonade, water
Cigar: tiparillo, siglo, cain, baccarat
1. Beverage:cola is on the right of Cigar:cain##1
2. Cigar:baccarat is on the far left##1
3. Cigar:cain is between Cigar:siglo and Beverage:juice##2
4. Beverage:water is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:lemonade is between Beverage:juice and Beverage:cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | water         | juice   | lemonade | cola       |
| Cigar      | baccarat | tiparillo | cain   | siglo |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: gardening, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
Job: analyst, engineer, manager, coach
1. Job:coach is between Hobby:reading and Job:engineer##2
2. Hobby:video-games is on the far right##1
3. Job:manager is on the right of Job:analyst##1
4. Hobby:gardening is on the left of Job:analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening | reading | video-games |
| Job   | engineer    | coach   | analyst | manager       |

