.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
Transport: trike, taxi, airplane, car
Nationality: australian, british, colombian, french
1. Nationality:colombian is on the right of Transport:car##1
2. Nationality:colombian is between Nationality:british and Transport:taxi##2
3. Nationality:british is on the far left##1
4. Nationality:french is on the left of Transport:airplane##1
5. Transport:taxi == Nationality:french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Transport          | car    | trike | taxi   | airplane  |
| Nationality   | british | colombian   | french | australian |

